st laptops’ screen space and is simple to set up and connect, and is lightweight enough to carry away when you’re done.</p>\n\n</div>","author":"","siteTitle":"Macworld","siteHash":"37e84dd5a21fa961d6d6630e269546024dbb7741b2e2fadbe74f47383c70dfbb","entryHash":"a5b70ffb3226f311a62d4e4779b67084c38914245a56894da77e667ced96c283","category":"Apple"}